text.tspan: Note: Only one ESP8266/LM75 is required when several 7 Segment Displays are interconnected
If using less than 3W per digit, 2 digits can share one buck converter. Full brightness is available up to 30s 20-30% of the time (e.g. 25s/180s cooldown)
Max. output power might be reduced if not properly cooled inside an enclosure
If single LEDs turn off, check output ripple at nearest output cap @ full brightness
